title: Women's Tennis Well Represented in Final Rounds of ITA Regionals (University of Kentucky)
text: ( Source : University of Kentucky ) WEST LAFAYETTE, Ind. - Kentucky 's women's tennis team continues to shine at the USTA / ITA Ohio Valley Regionals, as UK is one of two teams to have multiple competitors stay alive in the championship draws
